{
  "_comment": "==========================================================================",
  "_description": [
    "FHIR R4 — Medical Evolution Payload for AWS HealthLake",
    "This file shows the three FHIR resources sent as a Transaction Bundle",
    "when a professional saves a SOAP evolution in the HCOP (Problem-Oriented",
    "Medical Record).",
    "",
    "Resources included:",
    "  1. Encounter  — the consultation session",
    "  2. Condition  — the diagnosed problem (ICD-10 coded)",
    "  3. Observation (×4) — the four SOAP sections (S/O/A/P)",
    "",
    "AWS HealthLake endpoint pattern:",
    "  POST https://healthlake.<region>.amazonaws.com/datastore/<DATASTORE_ID>/r4",
    "  Headers:",
    "    Content-Type: application/fhir+json",
    "    Accept:       application/fhir+json",
    "  Auth: AWS Signature V4 (IAM role with AmazonHealthLakeFullAccess)"
  ],
  "_comment_end": "=========================================================================="
}
